Usage: optPower [-help] [-allowResizing] [-effortLevel {high}] [-force]
                [-postCts] [-postRoute] [-preCts] [-prePlace] [-seqOnly]

-help                                # Prints out the command usage
-allowResizing                       # Will only do sameSize/downSize/upSize
                                     # (bool, optional)
-effortLevel {high}                  # effort level option  (enum, optional)
-force                               # forced leakage opt (bool, optional)
-postCts                             # is postcts mode (bool, optional)
-postRoute                           # is postroute mode (bool, optional)
-preCts                              # is prects mode (bool, optional)
-prePlace                            # is prePlace mode (bool, optional)
-seqOnly                             # recover power with focus on flops
                                     # (bool, optional)